  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight, Adapt, and Survive.</strong> <i>BIORAGE </i>is an intense <strong>story-driven corridor FPS</strong> set in a fractured timeline where the force \"Freedom for All Rebellion\" clashes against the corporate empire \"Tempus Industries\". Experience <strong>15  levels across 5 visually stunning chapters</strong>. After the main character gets trapped by Tempus in a failed mission, you're left isolated—stranded between worlds seemingly colliding at your feet.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Main Story is about 1 hour long!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> – Battle through <strong>15 handcrafted levels</strong> with immersive storytelling and explosive action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warfare</strong> – You have plenty of guns, enemies and environments to challenge you alongside a soundtrack that will keep you going and make you feel awesome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Every previous version is accessible through Steam. For access, go to game page in library, gear icon, properties, and then game versions\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made with: First Person Shooter Creator - Black Ice Mod Advanced v3.4 beta 130125</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight, Adapt, and Survive.</strong> <i>BIORAGE </i>is an intense <strong>story-driven corridor FPS</strong> set in a fractured timeline where the force \"Freedom for All Rebellion\" clashes against the corporate empire \"Tempus Industries\". Experience <strong>15  levels across 5 visually stunning chapters</strong>. After the main character gets trapped by Tempus in a failed mission, you're left isolated—stranded between worlds seemingly colliding at your feet.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Main Story is about 1 hour long!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> – Battle through <strong>15 handcrafted levels</strong> with immersive storytelling and explosive action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warfare</strong> – You have plenty of guns, enemies and environments to challenge you alongside a soundtrack that will keep you going and make you feel awesome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Every previous version is accessible through Steam. For access, go to game page in library, gear icon, properties, and then game versions\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made with: First Person Shooter Creator - Black Ice Mod Advanced v3.4 beta 130125</p>",
